WEBVTT

00:03:59.375 --> 00:04:02.809
As a woman, I could not
be seen with a cell phone,

00:04:02.833 --> 00:04:05.726
so I used to huddle
his phone under my shawl

00:04:05.750 --> 00:04:08.643
and type as slowly as possible

00:04:08.667 --> 00:04:11.250
to ensure that I would not be heard.

00:04:13.167 --> 00:04:15.018
After many rounds of interviews,

00:04:15.042 --> 00:04:18.851
I got into the fellowship program
with a full scholarship.

00:04:18.875 --> 00:04:22.684
My father was confused,
my mother was worried --

00:04:22.708 --> 00:04:27.226
(Applause)

